      <a href="#ethicsContent" data-bs-toggle="collapse" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="ethicsContent">
        Trust & Ethics
      </a>
      <div class="collapse mt-2" id="ethicsContent">
        <p class="text-white-50 small mb-0">
          Our AI is governed by strict ethical principles to ensure fairness, neutrality, and transparency. We do not manipulate, promote, or suppress any candidate or voter. Only verified candidates can use insight tools or host mock elections. TrueVote’s mission is to support democratic processes through unbiased data and ethical technology.
